  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add soy sauce and garlic powder, stir for about 1 minute.",
    "Gently add frozen mixed vegetables to the pan, cover and cook until vegetables are heated through (about 5 minutes).",
    "Once vegetables are cooked, add red peppers, green onions, and almond slivers. Stir well until all ingredients are evenly coated in sauce.",
    "Serve warm with whole grain toast or as a side dish for breakfast."
